#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:360
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"The %2$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on "
"%3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Cast your vote:\n"
"\n"
"Vote YES (remove): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Vote NO (keep):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"A majority of active members (more than 50%%) must vote yes for the removal "
"to proceed. You can change your vote by clicking the other link before the "
"deadline.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Hai %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Komunitas %2$s telah membuka pemungutan suara untuk menghapus seorang "
"anggota. Pemungutan suara ditutup pada %3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Berikan suara Anda:\n"
"\n"
"Suara YA (hapus): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Suara TIDAK (pertahankan):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"Mayoritas anggota aktif (lebih dari 50%%) harus memilih ya agar penghapusan "
"dapat dilanjutkan. Anda dapat mengubah suara Anda dengan mengeklik tautan "
"lain sebelum tenggat waktu.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

