"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Tombol ikon yang membuka popover satu layar penuh yang berisi formulir "
"pendaftaran newsletter. Mandiri — langsung letakkan ke dalam header atau "
"bagian template footer; tidak menampilkan apa pun ketika newsletter publik "
"dinonaktifkan (Pengaturan → Newsletter)."

